data.clean_description: I ve had requests to put up a tip jar , so here it is. Although I do nt expect tips , I try to go out of my way to treat people well , and give as good of deals and as low of prices as I possibly can. And if you ve talked to me , you know I ll bend over backwards to help good people out in any way I can , so if for some reason you feel the need to say thanks here it is. OR hey , if for some reason you ve got an extra couple grand , or even million bucks or two that you do nt really want or is just sitting around collecting dust and you do nt know what to do with it , I ve set up another couple tip jars for thousand and million dollar tips too. Feel free to use those many many times D.
data.name: H2o $1 tip jar
